{"id":"zippor","term":"Zippor","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>A little bird, the father of Balak, king of Moab (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 22:2\">Num. 22:2</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 22:4\">4</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Numbers 22:2","Numbers 22:4"]}